doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(http-equiv='Content-Type', content='text/html; charset=UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1.0')
    title #{title} | Charles Truluck
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='css/materialize.css', type='text/css', rel='stylesheet', media='screen,projection')
    link(href='css/style.css', type='text/css', rel='stylesheet', media='screen,projection')
    script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.1.min.js')
    script(src='js/materialize.js')
    script(src='js/init.js')
  body
    nav.green(role='navigation')
      .nav-wrapper.container
        a#logo-container.brand-logo(href='#') #{title}
        ul.right.hide-on-med-and-down 
          li.waves-effect
            a(href='/wowilovebiomes') Home
          li.waves-effect
            a(href='/wowilovebiomes-faq') FAQs
          li.waves-effect
            a(href='/wowilovebiomes-planatrip') Things to Do
        ul#nav-mobile.side-nav
          li
            a.waves-effect(href='/wowilovebiomes') Home
          li
            a.waves-effect(href='/wowilovebiomes-faq') FAQs
          li
            a.waves-effect(href='/wowilovebiomes-planatrip') Things to Do
        a.button-collapse(href='#', data-activates='nav-mobile')
          i.material-icons menu
    .parallax-container(style="height:50%;")
     h1(style="padding-top:3%;").header.center.white-text Things to Do
     h5(style="font-weight:500;padding-bottom:3%;").header.center.col.s12.light.white-text What to see, where to go.
     .parallax
       img(src='forest.jpg' style="width: 100%;")
    br
    .container
      .main-content
        .row.center
          .col.s6
            .icon-block
              h2.center.green-text.text-darken-3
                i.material-icons map
              h5.center Map
              img(src="map_of_myanmar.jpg" style='width:100%;height:100%;') 
              a.waves-effect.waves-light.green.darken-3.btn(href='/wowilovebiomes-faq') More Info 
          .col.s6
            .icon-block
              h2.center.green-text.text-darken-3
                i.material-icons info_outline
              h5.center Hlawga National Park
              p.light
                | One of the most interesting sites of Myanmar is the Hlawga national park. It features a wide array of wild life to see, along with fun and cool activities. This park alone features 145 distinct bird species, and has a "mini zoo" which features tigers, mammels, birds, leopards and bears. The park is 1,540 Acres in area, and was established September 30, 1982
      br
      br
    footer.page-footer.green.darken-1
      .container
        .row
          .col.l6.s12
            h5.white-text About Myanmar Forest Services
            p.grey-text.text-lighten-4
              | At Myanmar Forest Services, we really care about our clients. That's why we offer the best housing, tours, sightseeing, and safety. We take pride in our work, and thats why you can trust us.
          .col.l3.s12
            h5.white-text Connect
            ul
              li
                a.white-text(href='http://twitter.com/charlestruluck_' target='_blank') Twitter
              li
                a.white-text(href='mailto:myanmarrainservices@ctruluck.com') Email
      .footer-copyright
        .container
          | &copy; 2016 Myanmar Forest Services | 
          a(href="https://github.com/charlestruluck/website") Source
    script.
      $(document).ready(function(){
        $('.parallax').parallax();
      });
